<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Sezione teoria -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-2xl mb-6">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
          Joseph va dal fruttivendolo con il papà per comprare delle arance.<br>
          Il fruttivendolo gli spiega alcune cose interessanti.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tre immagini con bilance -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <!-- Peso Lordo -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="p-3 bg-cyan-100 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 rounded-xl mb-3">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
              Il peso sulla bilancia non si riferisce solo alle arance, ma anche alla cassetta: è il <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">peso lordo</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p100/p100_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto rounded-lg", alt: "Bilancia 2,5 kg peso lordo" %>
        </div>

        <!-- Peso Netto -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="p-3 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 rounded-xl mb-3">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
              Il peso delle sole arance è il <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">peso netto</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p100/p100_02.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto rounded-lg", alt: "Bilancia 2 kg peso netto" %>
        </div>

        <!-- Tara -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="p-3 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/50 rounded-xl mb-3">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
              Il peso della cassetta si chiama <strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">tara</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p100/p100_03.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto rounded-lg", alt: "Bilancia 0,5 kg tara" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Definizioni e formule -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <!-- Peso Lordo -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">Peso lordo</strong>: peso della merce e del contenitore.
          </p>
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex gap-4 mb-2">
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">peso netto</div>
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">tara</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">+</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-cyan-500 text-white rounded font-bold">peso lordo</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Peso Netto -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Peso netto</strong>: peso della merce.
          </p>
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex gap-4 mb-2">
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">peso lordo</div>
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">tara</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">–</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-green-500 text-white rounded font-bold">peso netto</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tara -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Tara</strong>: peso del contenitore.
          </p>
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex gap-4 mb-2">
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">peso lordo</div>
              <div class="px-3 py-1 border-2 border-green-400 dark:border-green-600 rounded text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">peso netto</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">–</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded font-bold">tara</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testo esplicativo -->
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
        Quando si acquistano dei generi alimentari, di solito essi hanno un involucro o un contenitore.<br>
        Occorre allora distinguere il peso del prodotto confezionato (<strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">peso lordo</strong>), il peso del solo prodotto (<strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">peso netto</strong>) e il peso del contenitore (<strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">tara</strong>).
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Leggi le indicazioni di peso sulle etichette di alcuni prodotti e verifica con una bilancia!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Container esercizi -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-2xl">

      <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= imparare_tutti_badge(1) %>
          Leggi e colora la risposta giusta.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          Alessandro apre un barattolo nuovo di marmellata che pesa 375 g. Il barattolo vuoto pesa 25 g. Il peso netto della marmellata è:
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-3 rounded border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="es1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>400 g</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-3 rounded border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="es1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>350 g</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-3 rounded border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="es1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>325 g</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AllenaMente -->
      <div class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-blue-900/40 rounded-2xl border-3 border-blue-400 dark:border-blue-600">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-blue-300 mb-2">
          <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">AllenaMente!</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
          Una compagnia aerea ha stabilito che il bagaglio a mano non deve superare i 10 kg. Riccardo sta per partire. Verifica che i suoi vestiti pesino 10 kg e prepara la valigia. Arrivato in aeroporto gli dicono che il bagaglio non rispetta il peso prescritto. Prova a spiegare il perché.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/quaderno_link', pagine: [226, 234] %>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
